<i>Lithurgus chrysurus</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Fonscolombe, 1834</font></b><br>
<small><i>Lithurgus analis </i>Lepeletier, 1841; <i>Lithurgus haemorrhoidalis </i>Lepeletier, 1841; <i>Lithurgus chrysurus var siculus </i>P&#233;rez, 1897; <i>Lithurgus sublaevis </i>P&#233;rez, 1897; <i>Lithurgus &#40;Lithurgus&#41; chrysurus siculus </i>P&#233;rez, 1897</small><p>
